P.title: Will the Second Amendment of the United States Constitution be amended or repealed before 2025?
P.body:
Resolution Criteria
This question will resolve as Yes if, at any time between January 1, 2019 to January 1, 2025, the Second Amendment is repealed, amended, or modified in any way through the proceduce in Article Five of the US Constitution

not_P.title: Will the Second Amendment of the United States Constitution remain unchanged until 2025?
not_P.body:
Resolution Criteria
This question will resolve as Yes if, from January 1, 2019 to January 1, 2025, the Second Amendment is not repealed, amended, or modified in any way through the procedure in Article Five of the US Constitution

P.title: Will there be fewer than 6 conservative justices on the SCOTUS on January 20, 2025?
P.body:
Resolution Criteria
This question will resolve as Yes if on January 20, 2025, at noon EST, there are fewer than 6 conservative justices on the Supreme Court of the United States, as per reliable sources

not_P.title: Will there be 6 or more conservative justices on the SCOTUS on January 20, 2025?
not_P.body:
Resolution Criteria
This question will resolve as Yes if on January 20, 2025, at noon EST, there are 6 or more conservative justices on the Supreme Court of the United States, as per reliable sources

P.title: Will Pakistan recognize the Islamic Emirate of Afghanistan before 2030?
P.body:
Resolution Criteria
This question will resolve positively if before 01-01-2030, reliable media sources report that the Pakistani government has recognized the Islamic Emirate of Afghanistan

not_P.title: Will Pakistan not recognize the Islamic Emirate of Afghanistan before 2030?
not_P.body:
Resolution Criteria
This question will resolve positively if before 01-01-2030, reliable media sources do not report that the Pakistani government has recognized the Islamic Emirate of Afghanistan
